				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Orin has abductee Laezel, and is impersonating Laezel. Orin-as-Laezel has also taken Yenna hostage pretending to the players that Yenna is in fact Orin-in-disguise.\r\n\r\nDuring that camp-night confrontation, bad skill rolls or if players encouraged Orin-as-Laezel to kill Yenna, Yenna would be killed.\r\n\r\nThis PAD is played when the players approach her dead body after the encounter."
